<lyrics>[V1]
. D     Bm    G      A       D
 Jaqyndaǵym keledi Saǵan, Táńirim,
.D       Bm       G  A   D
 Aıqyshpen bolsa da kóterilsem.
. D         G             A        D
 Tek bir armanym bar: jaqyndasam Saǵan,
. G      D           G   A  D
 Jaqyndasam Táńirim, jaqyndasam.

[V2]
 Shól daladaǵy men jolaýshymyn,
 Qarańǵy túnde tas jastanamyn.
 Júregim árqashan Saǵan jaqyn,
 Táńirim. Saǵan jaqyn Táńirim, Saǵan jaqyn.

[V3]
 Oıanyp uıqymnan án salamyn,
 Maqtan etem Seni, jylamaımyn.
 Qaıǵyda qýanam jaqyndasam Saǵan.
 Jaqyndasam Táńirim, jaqyndasam.

[V4]
 Jerdegi ómirimdi bitirgende,
 Abyroıǵa meni bólegende,
 Máńgi qýanamyn, jaqyndasam Saǵan.
 Jaqyndasam Táńirim, jaqyndasam.</lyrics>
